Bigger than life

56:50.116 --> 56:55.413
Only happy endings

56:56.956 --> 57:01.252
That's our recipe

57:02.837 --> 57:04.756
So welcome

57:04.923 --> 57:08.676
To the movies

57:10.386 --> 57:12.847
Wait

57:13.014 --> 57:15.433
And

57:15.600 --> 57:17.519
See

