- She's taking her karate lesson.

01:13:11.430 --> 01:13:14.725
- Don't be nervous.
- I'm not. You give it to her.

01:13:14.975 --> 01:13:18.228
- It was your idea.
- She likes you more than me.

01:13:18.479 --> 01:13:21.607
Oliver, will you pull
yourself together!

01:13:27.696 --> 01:13:31.784
Want to see what the Asp
taught me today?

01:13:35.412 --> 01:13:38.248
To the couch, Punjab, if you please.

01:13:38.457 --> 01:13:42.127
- I didn't think it would work.
- Now you know it does.

01:13:42.377 --> 01:13:46.757
- Shall I call a doctor?
- It'll be fine.

01:13:55.641 --> 01:13:57.101
Thank you.

01:14:00.646 --> 01:14:02.856
