about something very serious.

01:14:19.790 --> 01:14:23.752
- You don't want me anymore.
- On the contrary, I do.

01:14:24.419 --> 01:14:25.754
Good Lord!

01:14:27.631 --> 01:14:31.218
- Can we have a man-to-man talk?
- Sure.

01:14:31.802 --> 01:14:36.098
