01:14:49.862 --> 01:14:53.031
I was born in Liverpool.

01:14:53.615 --> 01:14:58.745
My brother died of pneumonia because
we didn't have money for medicine.

01:15:00.414 --> 01:15:05.127
I decided then and there
that one day I would be very rich.

01:15:05.377 --> 01:15:09.715
- Good idea.
- America was the land of opportunity.

01:15:09.965 --> 01:15:13.343
I signed on a ship as cabin boy
when I was 12.

01:15:13.594 --> 01:15:17.556
By the time I was 21,
I'd made my first million.

01:15:17.806 --> 01:15:21.059
In the next 10 years,
I turned that into 100 million.

01:15:21.560 --> 01:15:26.440
In those days that was a lot
of money. I was ruthless.

01:15:27.191 --> 01:15:32.321
Making money was all I ever
gave a damn about, up to now.

01:15:34.364 --> 01:15:37.534
- Let's go inside.
- Okay.

01:15:40.704 --> 01:15:44.374
It has occurred to me that no matter
how many houses I have...

01:15:44.541 --> 01:15:46.001
...how many Rembrandts...

01:15:46.168 --> 01:15:52.174
...unless I have someone to share it
with, I might as well be broke.

01:15:52.341 --> 01:15:56.845
- Understand what I'm trying to say?
- Sure.

01:15:57.054 --> 01:15:58.222
Kind of.

01:15:58.430 --> 01:16:00.766
- Kind of?
- I guess not.

01:16:00.933 --> 01:16:04.061
Damn! Oh, excuse me.

01:16:12.819 --> 01:16:17.241
- You've given me so much already.
